00:18:03,333 --> 00:18:04,875
calculating the
path to the scene.

259
00:18:04,958 --> 00:18:06,250
Put it up on the screen.

260
00:18:07,083 --> 00:18:08,583
Gourai-Go's preparations?

261
00:18:08,666 --> 00:18:10,541
It'll be complete
in 60 seconds.

262
00:18:10,625 --> 00:18:12,208
Flower Division members
have starting boarding

263
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:13,666
into their Koubu Kai's.

264
00:18:19,958 --> 00:18:20,875
Ignition complete.

265
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:22,041
Yours truly
ready for dispatch.

266
00:18:22,125 --> 00:18:24,291
Maria Tachibana,
ready for dispatch.

267
00:18:33,583 --> 00:18:35,291
Sakura unit ignition complete.

268
00:18:35,375 --> 00:18:37,291
Koubu Kai's ignition
is... complete.

269
00:18:37,375 --> 00:18:39,083
Right, begin loading!

270
00:19:00,083 --> 00:19:01,333
Begin loading.

271
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:42,416
Moving engine into position.

272
00:19:49,916 --> 00:19:51,166
Rotation complete!

273
00:20:16,583 --> 00:20:18,500
All levels are green.
