for reminding me of this?!

1053
01:16:44,625 --> 01:16:47,791
We've laughed together
fought and dreamed together...

1054
01:16:47,875 --> 01:16:50,041
And you and I have
shared even more than that!

1055
01:16:50,125 --> 01:16:52,416
We've appreciated this place.

1056
01:16:52,500 --> 01:16:53,833
And - I...

1057
01:16:53,916 --> 01:16:55,208
And I

1058
01:16:55,291 --> 01:16:56,333
You see...

1059
01:16:56,416 --> 01:16:58,583
I love you so!

1060
01:16:58,666 --> 01:17:00,791
Oh...

1061
01:17:10,166 --> 01:17:13,458
My dear Prince, with all due
respect, will slaying your

1062
01:17:13,541 --> 01:17:15,958
defenseless wife lift a
burden from your heart?

1063
01:17:16,041 --> 01:17:18,541
Let me be the target
of your rage.

1064
01:17:18,625 --> 01:17:21,166
My friends, companions,
comrades...

1065
01:17:21,250 --> 01:17:25,041
Alas-I can feel my heart
turn cold as ice!!

1066
01:17:25,125 --> 01:17:27,541
This world is rife
with enemies!

1067
01:17:27,625 --> 01:17:29,875
As you stand here before
us all, you have shared

1068
01:17:29,958 --> 01:17:32,666
your heart and
your deepest desires.

1069
01:17:32,750 --> 01:17:34,791
And if what you say is
true; that you desire

1070
01:17:34,875 --> 01:17:36,750
my life most of all...

1071
01:17:36,833 --> 01:17:39,416
Know that I would
gladly give it to you.

1072
01:17:39,500 --> 01:17:40,875
I commend your strength.

1073
01:17:40,958 --> 01:17:43,791
Now resign yourself
to a death by my hands!

1074
01:17:45,666 --> 01:17:49,291
I, for the want of making my
power felt, conspired with

1075
01:17:49,375 --> 01:17:51,291
the demons of the land,
in an attempt

1076
01:17:51,375 --> 01:17:53,625
to bring chaos to this world!

1077
01:17:53,708 --> 01:17:55,541
I now have no place to return.

1078
01:17:55,625 --> 01:17:57,958
With your death followed
by mine ' let us venture

1079
01:17:58,041 --> 01:18:00,041
into the netherworld together.

1080
01:18:01,208 --> 01:18:04,166
Cast your hatred upon me
dear Princess!

1081
01:18:05,958 --> 01:18:08,541
I harbor no hatred at all.

1082
01:18:08,625 --> 01:18:11,041
For hatred only
breeds further hatred.

1083
01:18:11,125 --> 01:18:13,666
So you see...

1084
01:18:13,750 --> 01:18:15,875
I can forgive you with
all of my heart.

1085
01:18:15,958 --> 01:18:17,791
I forgive you.

1086
01:18:26,500 --> 01:18:28,083
I too forgive you.

1087
01:18:28,166 --> 01:18:29,875
And I forgive you.

1088
01:18:29,958 --> 01:18:31,708
I also forgive you.

1089
01:18:31,791 --> 01:18:33,375
I forgive you.

1090
01:18:33,458 --> 01:18:35,125
I forgive you.

1091
01:18:35,208 --> 01:18:36,666
I forgive you.

1092
01:18:36,750 --> 01:18:40,125
I forgive you too as well.

1093
01:18:40,208 --> 01:18:43,208
I will not be deceived
by this farcical story!

1094
01:18:43,291 --> 01:18:46,750
I shall bring down the curtain
and in doing so end this story!

1095
01:18:46,833 --> 01:18:49,041
But must this be the end?

1096
01:18:49,125 --> 01:18:51,208
Do you really think that
by lowering the curtain

1097
01:18:51,291 --> 01:18:53,708
that it will end all stories?

1098
01:18:53,791 --> 01:18:54,875
As long as...

1099
01:18:54,958 --> 01:18:56,833
As long as people are alive...

1100
01:18:56,916 --> 01:19:00,041
... Their stories will be heard
and will never end.

1101
01:19:03,750 --> 01:19:06,208
That is enough.

1102
01:19:06,291 --> 01:19:09,708
The time has finally come
to slay this story!!

1103
01:19:24,166 --> 01:19:25,916
I...

1104
01:19:26,000 --> 01:19:27,291
I...

1105
01:19:43,708 --> 01:19:45,166
I cannot.

1106
01:19:45,250 --> 01:19:50,750
I can't bring myself to slay
my love-my friends or dreams!

1107
01:19:50,833 --> 01:19:53,416
The blood I shed my prince,
it is your blood.

1108
01:19:53,500 --> 01:19:56,250
All of the blood of hatred
flows out to the sea and now

1109
01:19:56,333 --> 01:19:58,666
a new story has been
born in it's place.

1110
01:19:58,750 --> 01:20:00,333
For just a little longer...

1111
01:20:00,416 --> 01:20:02,583
 I wanted this moment to last.

1112
01:20:02,666 --> 01:20:05,500
I found contentment in
holding onto such a wish.

1113
01:20:05,583 --> 01:20:07,916
There are as many different
stories as there are people...

1114
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:10,958
and each one
blossoms like a flower.

1115
01:20:11,041 --> 01:20:13,083
Flowers now appear before us.

1116
01:20:13,166 --> 01:20:16,041
For here and now, there are
many flowers; like dreams,

1117
01:20:16,125 --> 01:20:18,833
that will blossom
again and again!

1118
01:20:18,916 --> 01:20:22,708
And they will unfold their
blooms with the light of life.

